Package: bayespulse
Type: Package
Title:
    Bayesian model for pulsatile hormone concentration data
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: c(
      person("Matt", "Mulvahill", email = "matt@mulvahill.com", role = c("cre", "aut")),
      person("Nichole", "Carlson", email = "nichole.carlson@ucdenver.edu", role = c("aut", "cph", "ths")))
Description:
    Bayesian deconvolution for pulsatile hormone secretion using birth-death MCMC.
    Provides single-subject analysis, hierarchical population models, and joint
    driver-response hormone models. Includes MCMC diagnostics and visualization tools.
URL: https://github.com/mmulvahill/libpulsatile
BugReports: https://github.com/mmulvahill/libpulsatile/issues
